<p>
<lb n="1"/>svastiśrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> Eṟika 
<lb n="2" break="no"/>lmutturājulṟu 
<lb n="3"/>kuṇḍikāḷu nivarikā 
<lb n="4" break="no"/>nu Iccina pannasa 
<lb n="5"/>dujayarājula 
<lb n="6"/>muturājulu nava 
<lb n="7"/>priya muturājulu 
<lb n="8"/>vallava dukarājulu <unclear>śa</unclear> kṣi 
<lb n="9"/>kanu Iccina pannassa 
</p>

<!--<h4>SECOND FACE.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="10"/>koṭṭaṁbuna pā 
<lb n="11"/>ḻaku kuṇḍikāḷlu 
<lb n="12"/>ḷa Iccina pannasa 
<lb n="13"/>Iruvadi yādi nā 
<lb n="14" break="no"/>ṭkamaṟutuṟḻunēla <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> 
</p>

